data.description: Magnificent Full Brick Home with Finished Basement on Almost 1 acre!! These spacious home features a Great Room, Dinning Room, Laundry, 3 bedrooms & Full Bath on the main floor. The Finished Basement could be used as a 2nd Living Quarter featuring a Family Room, Bonus/Flex Room and Full Bath with access from the interior and exterior of the home. This fabulous home also has a 2 car garage, located on a corner lot surrounded by mature trees for convenient privacy. Ideal Location near Uptown Lincoln, Local Shopping, Restaurants, and Excellent Schools.
